# NBA NO FOMO

 NBA NO FOMO is a page that assigns a FOMO score to all NBA games over the next week. The FOMO score is a 0-100 scale that estimates how fun, entertaining, and worth watching a game will be. If you're not sure what game to watch, consult NBA NO FOMO!

Click on a game to reveal some of the underlying data behind each score. You can read a full explanation of the score methodology [here](about).

And if you find this useful, consider donating to me! (I'm broke)
